{2000}{}{Yes? What, what is it?}
{2010}{}{Sebastian sent me. I've got a delivery for you.}
{2020}{}{What do you do around here?}
{2030}{}{Could I buy some medical supplies?}
{2040}{}{Got any work for me?}
