{3000}{}{You do? Perfect. Let me see that. (He snatches the briefcase)}
{3010}{}{Well, it looks like my work here is done.}
{3020}{}{Am I gonna get paid for this?}
{4000}{}{(He ignores you) Let's take a look here...propoxin, hydrozapam, alprazaline, dilaftin... not great, but it'll do. Alright, you did good. Go see Sebastian, he probably has something for you.}
